class ExtParams(Parameters):
    defaults = extend_ex_path
    label_to_extend = 'd0'
    array_first = True
params = ExtParams()
params.adjust({'extend_param': [{'d0': 3, 'value': -1}]}, clobber=False)
assert params.extend_param.tolist() == [[1, 2], [1, 2], [1, 2], [-1, -1], [
    -1, -1], [5, 6], [5, 6], [7, 8], [7, 8], [7, 8], [7, 8]]
params = ExtParams()
params.adjust({'extend_param': [{'d0': 3, 'd1': 'c1', 'value': -1}, {'d0': 
    3, 'd1': 'c2', 'value': 1}]}, clobber=False)
assert params.extend_param.tolist() == [[1, 2], [1, 2], [1, 2], [-1, 1], [-
    1, 1], [5, 6], [5, 6], [7, 8], [7, 8], [7, 8], [7, 8]]
params = ExtParams()
params.adjust({'extend_param': [{'d0': 3, 'value': -1}, {'d0': 5, 'd1':
    'c1', 'value': 0}, {'d0': 5, 'd1': 'c2', 'value': 1}, {'d0': 8, 'd1':
    'c1', 'value': 22}, {'d0': 8, 'd1': 'c2', 'value': 23}]}, clobber=False)
assert params.extend_param.tolist() == [[1, 2], [1, 2], [1, 2], [-1, -1], [
    -1, -1], [0, 1], [0, 1], [7, 8], [22, 23], [22, 23], [22, 23]]
params = ExtParams()
params.adjust({'extend_param': [{'d0': 3, 'value': -1}, {'d0': 5, 'd1':
    'c1', 'value': 0}, {'d0': 6, 'd1': 'c2', 'value': 1}]}, clobber=False)
assert params.extend_param.tolist() == [[1, 2], [1, 2], [1, 2], [-1, -1], [
    -1, -1], [0, 6], [0, 1], [7, 8], [7, 8], [7, 8], [7, 8]]
params = ExtParams()
params.adjust({'extend_param': [{'d0': 0, 'value': 1}]}, clobber=False)
assert params.extend_param.tolist() == [[1, 1], [1, 1], [1, 2], [3, 4], [3,
    4], [5, 6], [5, 6], [7, 8], [7, 8], [7, 8], [7, 8]]
